title: Live Camera Viewer â˜… World Webcam & IP Cam Streams
description:
This cool app has been downloaded by superheroes to hurry up and save the world! :)
View people, pets (including pandas, dolphins, sharks!), traffic, cities, weather condtions on more than 60,000 public live real time online video streaming CCTV surveillance and security web cameras around the world right from your Android smartphone and tablet. Watch almost every place on Earth on live cams in our webcam viewer (we add every Earth cam by your requests inside the app). Have a live streaming webcam video from everywhere in the world, always! Great worldview for travelers to have a spy sneak peek at travel destinations.
With Live Camera Viewer you can:
â€¢ Search cams by keywords in every country, like United States, UK, Canada, Germany, Australia, Russia, Ukraine
â€¢ Select cams by Country, HD, Category like cities, weather, traffic, restaurants, offices, zoos, airports, beaches, etc.
â€¢ Like and vote for the best cameras, customize your cam collection
â€¢ Zoom live video with motion controls on your Android smartphone and tablet
â€¢ Save camera shots
Use free Live Camera Viewer to:
â€¢ Make holiday or family vacation travel plans with weather forecast
â€¢ Study world cultures, geography, logistics and economics
â€¢ See animals play and study animal behavior (yes, we've got lots of live web cameras with animals)
â€¢ Find and watch familiar places in your own city, like clubs, bars, restaurants, malls, shops, hotels, banks etc.
â€¢ Receive live news, events, weather monitoring, road auto traffic and jam information
â€¢ Have fun with friends, prank, play and imagine being security guard or enjoy as hacker simulator performing joke hack ;-)
Leave a review at the Google Play with your wishes and feature requests!

title: Indian Railways train enquiry
description:
PNR Status, Live running train status, Seat availability, Train schedule, Coach locator, Flights, Hotels, top holiday places and much more, all packed in one app !
Indian Railways app is loaded with much more features than any other railway enquiry app in the store.
Indian Railways app has the following key features:-
1) PNR Status of a booked Ticket which can be saved for later view and ability to refresh it anytime.
2) Trains Arriving at a Station within specified hours
3) Live Running Status of the Train from ntes with advanced Map view.
4) Easily check Train Route / schedule . Future requests for the same train schedule won't require internet !
5) Fare Inquiry with tatkal option
6) Search all reserved and unreserved Trains between two stations
7) Best feature is advanced seat availability which fetches seat availability for all trains between two given stations in just one click ! Also check Train availability 6 days post the desired date
8) Explore 2,000+ Top Holiday destinations in India with Photos, Reviews and much more posted by real Travelers
9) Coach Map showing various classes in train like 1A , 2A , 3A , SL , Double Decker , GaribRath etc.
10) Show Diverted Trains for Today.
11) Show Re-Scheduled Trains for Today.
12) Show Cancelled Trains for Today.
13) IRCTC train ticket booking can be done superfast ! Now book railway tickets within minutes through irctc website right from within the app.
14) Share PNR status , train seat availability , train route & train status results to your friends via SMS, Email, etc
15) Auto PNR tracker which notifies you of any changes with your irctc booked railway ticket.
16) Compare over 50K+ Hotels & get best deals on hotels in India from 50+ booking partners !
You can now plan your holiday amongst the top holiday places in India and get the best hotels deals for the same.Find hotel amenities, see photos of rooms, read ratings and reviews and access location & maps.
17) Local and Metro for Mumbai and Delhi Metro trains can be searched from within the app.
18) Train bogie / Coach position can be easily checked from the app.
19) Find trains with train numbers and names
20) This app covers all major trains in India, including: Shatabdi Express, Rajdhani, Duronto Express, Garib Rath, Jan Shatabdi, Inter-city, Superfast Trains & Local MEMU / EMU Trains, Suburban Trains
21) Search & compare air flight fares across 100+ leading airline websites and travel portals and find cheapest airline tickets - Top airlines including Jet Airways Indigo, Spicejet, Go Air, Vistara, Air Asia, Air India, Lufthansa, KLM, Emirates, Singapore Airlines & many more worldwide carriers !
Disclaimer: Indian railways app is not affiliated to irctc / ntes / Railways and there are no warranties associated with the app. By using this app, you are solely responsible for any legal implications/liabilities arising from using the app.
You may have to visit the official Indian Railways, IRCTC or NTES train website / apps to make your bookings.

title: Tripoto Travel App: Plan Trips
description:
Tripoto is a unique travel app to discover real travel itineraries written by real travellers, with real route maps, photos and guides. Discover more than 20000+ places to visit in India and 200000+ more in the world. Get inspired to travel more with this travel app & trip planner.
Already a traveller? Create your own travel blog in the world's largest community of travel bloggers and share your travel experiences and trips with millions of travellers in the world.
Tripoto is one of the best travel apps for discovering holidays, hidden travel destinations, around the world or in places near you. Tripoto helps you plan your vacation or weekend getaways to places where real travellers have been, through real travel guides to discover something new in thousands of places to visit in the world.
Tripoto's FREE travel app is easy to use for Travel & Local information, with many cool features to plan your next trip. 2.5 million+ people use the Tripoto Travel App to read and share travel tips, backpacking guides, solo trip itineraries.
Here's what you can do on this Travel App
Trip Planner-See where other travellers have been and plan your vacation to amazing places to visit in the world or find places near you. This travel app allows you to plan trip itineraries to 10000s of destinations with backpacking ideas, weekend getaways, authentic tours or search for hidden places to visit in the world. Find the perfect place to go for holiday in India or anywhere in the world.
Travel Blogs-Start your own travel blog to share your travel stories with the world. Or see the world through the eyes of 1000s of travel bloggers on the Tripoto Community. Been backpacking through europe or paragliding in New Zealand? Share your vacation on your very own travel blog on Tripoto
Connect with Travellers-Tripoto is the world's largest community of travel bloggers. Connect with travel enthusiasts, holiday-makers, backpackers and solo travellers and create your own social travel circle. Create your very own travel blog to share your own travel stories.

Find places by your interests, region, season and budget. From backpacking trips to luxury vacations, get inspired to travel no matter what your travel style.
Use "Near Me Now" to find places to visit, things to do, vacation spots and hotels, hostels, resorts and homestays to plan your accommodation in your trip itinerary
Search for Hotels, Resorts, Things to do, Tourist Attractions, Sightseeing, Day-Trips, Walking Tours to explore cities and to get to know them better, Treks and much more
Route Plannerâ€“Map your Journey and Routes. Find transport in the remotest corners of the world to suit all budgets. The route planner includes public transportation, including trains, buses, ferries and taxis in 40000+ cities in the world
Get weather information for 40000+ places
Travel Guides of Places to Visit in India:
North Goa, South Goa Tours & Travel Guide

Weekend Getaways from Delhi

Road Trips

Honeymoon Ideas
We hope you enjoy this travel app. Happy travelling!

title: Indian Railway Time Table PRO
description:
Rail Guru is one of its kind of app having indian railway timetable, pnr status, fare calculator, train live status, seat availability, seat map, passing trains and many more.
Got slow or no Internet. No Problem Indian railway info can work Offline
# No Internet Required.
indian railway time table is best railway app
It's fast and reliable it has everything that you can ever need.
# It's Free. and always will be.
1. Train between two railway stations
2. PNR status for your ticket Just Enter the 10 digit pnr number and get your live booking status online or by sms.
2. Seat availability (including tatkal ticket)
3. Fare (including all classes)
4. Live Station - Trains Arriving at a Station within specified hours
5. Seat map / berth layout
6. Coach / rake position - Locate your Boggie on platform.
7. Share your train running status, pnr status, seat availability, fare and many more.
8. Train detailed info like :
Run days - days on which train runs.
Class - classes that train have like 1A, 2A, 3A, SL, CC, FC etc.
Pantry - check if train has catering facility
Fare Includes food cost - check if fare includes food.
Total travel time - total runtime of a particular train.
Advance reservation period (ARP) - Check how early can you book seat
Rake share - Check what other trains share the boggies of particular train.

title: Indian Railways Enquiry IRCTC
description:
Indian Railways Enquiry (IRCTC) App is a free resource for train travelers. PNR
A app for Indian Railways Services like PNR Status Enquiry, Berth/Seat Availability, Train Running Enquiry, Live Station etc.
The app offers various services to the Indian Railways user such as
â–º  PNR Status Enquiry of your booked tickets
â–º  Trains Between Two Stations (Source and Destination)
â–º  Seat/Berth Availability in Indian Railways between two Stations for ticket booking
â–º  Trains Arriving / Departing at a Station (Live Station) Arrivals Departures
â–º  Option to query all currently running trains going towards a Station or Direction from a particular station
â–º  Fare Enquiry / Ticket Cost including Tatkal Tickets
â–º  Train Schedule / Train Time Table
â–º  Spot your train / Present position of any train along with Delays on map
â–º  Current Booking Seat/Berth Availability after chart preparation
â–º  Coach Position at platform
â–º  Quick Availability of seats from a Station for Next 7 Days
â–º  Search for local, Suburban or Metro trains in metropolitan cities like Delhi, Mumbai, Chennai, Bangalore, Hyderabad, Kolkata, Jaipur, Pune etc.
â–º  Amenities Near Station such as Hotels, ATMs , Restaurants, and Hospitals including IRCTC outlet information for train food services.
â–º  Informs about the direction to reach Hotel from Station helpful facility to know taxi and auto fares.
â–º  Current speed of the train with five nearest stations
â–º  Get destination alarm to give alerts before the train actually reaches the selected station.
â–º  Menu card from the IRCTC which is applicable on all Mail/Express Trains running on the Indian Railway Network
All the above services are sourced from IRCTC
Large UI to help Senior Travelers of Indian Railway with complete information; PNR enquiry option remembers last searched PNR No for ease of query for all RailYatri
PNR Status Enquiry: All reservations or bookings done on the Indian Rail or IRCTC Connect app receive a unique PNR identification. This information is sourced from IRCTC servers.
Seat and Berth Availability for all the classes shown in table view form for ease of traveler.
Spot your train option gives live train status as well as Map View to help you know the train route. If you want to know the latest and accurate seat availability status, then this app provides you with the required info from IRCTC. This app provides a Jugaad to search for the best Seats available.
Live Station (Arrivals and Departures): Daily travelers get information on all the trains arriving or departing from a particular station within the next 2/4/6/8 hrs. Helps local up-downers with information on trains departing from the station which include - Mumbai local train, EMU, DEMU, and Passenger trains. This app provides this information directly from IRCTC servers.
Trains between stations: There are so many trains plying on the Indian Railways network, this app helps you to filter/search the exact train you are looking for. and all this comes from IRCTC servers.
Railways rules and regulation about baggage allowed, ticket cancellation refund etc. We also provide information about coach layout so that you can know whether you got a window seat or an upper berth or the middle berth.
Suburban Metro Maps (Offline) â€“ Includes route maps of Mumbai Local, Delhi Metro - DMRC, Hyderabad MMTS, Bangalore (Namma) Metro, Chennai Metro & suburban and Kolkata Metro & Suburban. Being authentic IRCTC info, you can count on this.
Coach Position: You can accurately get information about the exact sequence of coaches in any train. This information is also sourced from IRCTC and National Train Enquiry System NTES servers.
Destination Alarm is a new feature added to the app.
Another feature recently added to the app is online monitoring of all running trains on a map.
Disclaimer: The info provided in this app is sourced from publicly available sources, but we are not in any way affiliated to IRCTC or Indian Railways or NTES.

title: IRCTC Rail Connect - for RAIL SAARTHI
description:
App should be download in combination with RAIL SAARTHI app available at google play store
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cris.uima
Welcome to IRCTC Rail Connect App for Android.
IRCTC Rail ticketing now made simpler just by SWIPE and SHUFFLE, SELECT and BOOK. Install the newly launched "IRCTC RAIL CONNECT" android app and book a railway ticket anywhere in India at your fingertips.
Preview the latest features in addition to existing ticketing services:
:: New Users, register and activate from App directly.
:: Advanced security features of self-assigned PIN to login without entering username and password on each login.
:: Supports Ladies,Tatkal & Premium-Tatkal quota booking.
:: Current reservation facility.
:: Integrated with IRCTC e-wallet for faster and hassle free transactions.

:: Users can view the status of e-tickets booked through our authorized Online Travel Agents (OTA).
:: Users can view and cancel old mobile app tickets also.
Give early feedback: Let us know what you think and help improvements in IRCTC Rail Connect Android App.
Enjoy the never before experience of online ticketing with all new IRCTC Rail Connect Mobile App.

title: UTS MOBILE TICKETING
description:
Paperless ticket has been enabled in entire Chennai suburban section, entire Mumbai suburban section and New Delhi - Palwal section, in continuation of Paperless ticket now Season and Platform Tickets are introduced. In addition to that, now 'Change Handset' feature is introduced which is used to Change passenger old handset to new one, and active Season Ticket will transferred from old handset to new one.
Using 'show ticket' feature the ticket can be showed to the TTE(Travelling Ticket Examiner) or TC. Off-line mode is available to show the paperless ticket if Internet connection not available in the mobile.

title: Google Street View
description:
Explore world landmarks, discover natural wonders, and step inside locations such as museums, arenas, restaurants, and small businesses with Google Street View.
You can also add your own Street View for everyone to see. Create 360 photos using either your phone's camera or a certified Street View Ready camera, then position them and add connections on the map using the Street View app.
New for Local Guides level 6+ and Street View Trusted Photographers:
Try the new "Video Mode" beta, where you can connect a Ricoh Theta V camera and create Street View as you walk, bike, or drive. This new mode records video from your camera and converts it into connected Street View images when you publish to Google Maps.
APP REQUIRES ANDROID 4.4 KITKAT AND UP

title: IndianRailway Offline TimeTabl
description:
Access railway time table anywhere, anytime without being connected to internet. This application is like a printed railway time table in your pocket.
1. Train list from source to destination for a day or week.
2. Passing by trains through station for a day or week.
3. Train complete route.
4. Application and database gets stored on SD card so main memory required for this app is very less.
[NOTE: Database file has to be downloaded.  Size of DB file is around 3 MB. Request you to download the DB while having good internet connection like WIFI or 3G. With GPRS connection also it works but may be very slow. You can also check for updates. You can download the database to stay uptodate.]
Additional features:
* Train online status
* PNR status
* The complete travel app for India
* Included near stations and checkbox for Bangalore, Delhi, Mumbai, Kolkata, Chennai, Hyderabad, Tirupati, Trivendrum, Kochin, Goa, Lucknow, Varanasi, Patna, Nagpur, Chandrapur, Bhopal, Mangalore.
* Save paper and environment by using this electronic time table.
* We have seperate applications for local trains of Mumbai, Chennai, Kolkata and Hyderabad.  Please download and use those applications if you need time table of local trains for those cities.

title: Google Trips - Travel Planner
description:
Google Trips makes exploring the world easier by organizing your essential info in one place and making it available even offline. Get activity suggestions based on whatâ€™s nearby, customizeable day plans, and your travel reservations from Gmail.
AUTOMATIC TRIP ORGANIZATION
Your travel reservations are automatically gathered from Gmail and organized into individual trips. Each trip contains day plans, things to do, food and drink suggestions, and more.
BUNDLED RESERVATIONS
See your flight, hotel, rental car, and restaurant bookings in one place without having to search for them individually.
DAY PLANS
For several hundred of the worldâ€™s top places, find popular day plans organized on a map that you can customize based on your interests and available time.
NEARBY ATTRACTIONS
Find out when youâ€™re near popular attractions (and whether theyâ€™re open) as well as reviews and ratings from other travelers.
THINGS TO DO
Every trip contains ideas for things to do automatically organized into useful categories like Top Spots and Indoors or Outdoors. For many of the worldâ€™s top places, youâ€™ll get curated local suggestions and travel tips.
OFFLINE ACCESS
No Internet? No problem. Google Trips is available offline, so youâ€™ll always have access to your info.

title: ONN Bikes - Bike Rentals
description:
ONN Bikes is a self-ride motorbike rental platform. Covering major cities in India, ONN Bikes is the most affordable bike rental service where you can rent two-wheelers on an hourly, daily, weekly and monthly subscription. From your daily intra-city commute to your inter-city travel plans â€“ ONN Bikes with its super economical pricing aims to create an alternate mode of commute in India.
It is extremely easy to rent a bike of your choice form ONN Bikes â€“ Here is how it works:-
â€¢ Location: - Open the app and select the location from where you would like to pick-up the vehicle. If you fall into our delivery zone, you will be eligible for free delivery. You can enter the location in the location tab, or let the app detect your current location. Depending on your choice, you can either chose to pick-up the vehicle from our station or press â€˜Deliveryâ€™ tab if the option is activated.
â€¢ Date & Time: - Choose the start and end date/time of your booking. You will be charged based on the duration for which you wish to rent the vehicle from ONN Bikes.
â€¢ Select Bike:- The next screen will show you the available bike models for the selected location and time duration entered by you. The screen will also show the tariff and the security deposit to be paid for the respective bike. Please note that the deposit has to be paid while taking the delivery of the bike. You only have to pay the tariff amount through the application to book the bike.
â€¢ Confirmation Screen: - This screen will give you all the necessary details related to your booking. The user is requested to read the terms and conditions thoroughly before proceeding further. Once you agree to the â€˜Terms of Useâ€™, you will be directed to the payment page.
â€¢ Payment: - You can make the payment via Paytm, Debit card, Credit card or Net Banking.
â€¢ Booking Confirmation: - After successful completion of payment, your booking will be confirmed. This screen will show all the details related to your booking.
Security Deposit: -Please note that the security deposit will be refunded at the time of vehicle return. In case of any damages or late return, penalty charges will be applicable and the same will be deducted from the security deposit. Please refer to the Pricing Policy in case of any queries.
Driving License: - Please note that it is mandatory to have a valid Driving License in order to rent a bike from ONN Bikes. The license copy can be uploaded to the application while booking or while taking the delivery of the vehicle.
Menu Options:-
My Bookings: -This option will show you details of your existing and past bookings.
Offers and Deals: - You can check out all the running offers and deals on the ONN Bikes application in the menu section. Make the most of all the offers and discounts while booking your ride.
Report Accident: - In case of an accident or an emergency situation, you can directly call the ambulance service from this menu option.
Call Support: - You can directly call our customer care center using this option.
Refer and Earn: - ONN Bikes has launched â€˜Refer and Earnâ€™ program. If you like our service, do not miss the opportunity to earn credit points by referring to your friends. These credits can be used for your next booking from ONN Bikes.
Pricing and Models: - You can check out our fleet details along with the pricing details by clicking on this option.
Our Policy: - You can read our Privacy Policy, Terms of Use and Pricing Policy by clicking on this tab.
Follow us on Facebook at https://www.facebook.com/onnbikes
Follow us on Twitter at https://twitter.com/OnnBikes
Follow us on Instagram at https://www.instagram.com/onnbikes/
Do not forget to rate our application experience in the APP store.

title: NoteCam Lite- photo with notes
description:
Have you ever forgotten a place in a photo? Have you ever forgotten a person in a photo? NoteCam can solve this problem.
NoteCam is a camera App combined with GPS information (including latitude, longitude, altitude and accuracy), time, and comments. It can leave a message, and put all information together into a photograph. When you browse the photos, you can quickly know their location and their further information.
For more information, please refer to the following document.
http://notecam.derekr.com/download/Introduction_EN_20180223.pdf
â–  The difference between "NoteCam Lite" and "NoteCam Pro."
(1) NoteCam Lite is a free App. NoteCam Pro is a paid App.
(2) NoteCam Lite has a "Powered by NoteCam" text (watermark) in photographs' bottom right corner.
(3) NoteCam Pro can use the text watermark or the graphic watermark.
(4) NoteCam Pro can import a user-defined font file.
(5) Both are ad-free.

title: Meru Cabs- Local, Rental, Outstation, Airport Taxi
description:
Riding around the city 24X7 just got simpler, faster and convenient, with the all new Meru App. Now travel cashless in Bangalore, Delhi, Hyderabad, Mumbai, Pune, Ahmedabad, Jaipur, Chennai, and Kolkata. Pay by cash, multiple in-app wallets or Bharat QR code for your local, airport and intercity tours.
**Authorized Airport transfer services, offline counters also available in major cities.
For any kind of travel â€œBook nowâ€ or â€œBook (for) laterâ€ up to 7 days, from our wide fleet of sedan, hatchback and SUV cars.
Our popular travel options are -
1. Local â€“ Hail a ride locally within the city, airport, railway station using our reliable city taxis
2. Rental - Long trip with multiple stops, Try our flexible hourly/full â€“day/half day packages
3. Outstation - One way or return commute between cities at affordable tariffs
Now book Meru for business, visit our website (https://www.meru.in/corporate) for more details.
Follow these easy steps to book a Meru -
For instant ride:
Open the app >> Select to â€˜Book nowâ€™ >> Set your destination >> Click on the most suitable ride basis their ETA, fare, model and rating >> Place the booking
For scheduling your ride up to next 7 days:
Open the app >> Select to â€˜Book laterâ€™ >> Set your route >> Choose from exact fare as calculated by ExactoMeter or Normal Fare estimation >> Place the booking
You can set your payment mode as â€˜Cashâ€™ or â€˜Walletâ€™ of your choice. Pay using multiple in-app wallets (Paytm/ MobiKwik/ FreeCharge/ Citrus/ JioMoney) or Bharat QR Code.
What makes Meru uber-cool?
â€¢ True Marketplace: The only cab app that enables our driver-partners to set their own fare in a given range and compete amongst themselves, ensuring that you get the best deal for your ride. And you get to select your cab ride based on lowest fare, lowest ETA, highest driver rating and car model, even before you book a ride.
â€¢ Multiple ride options: Wide range of Hatchbacks, Sedans, SUVs to choose from for local, outstation or rental services
â€¢ Track your cab: Track the real-time status of your taxi cab.
â€¢ Know your driver: Once you book a cab, get detailed information about driver along his photograph.
â€¢ Travel cashless: Pay via multiple in-app wallets such as Paytm, MobiKwik, Freecharge, Citrus and Jio Money, Bharat QR code. Also, now available â€˜Pay Laterâ€™ option powered by Simpl
â€¢ Online payment even for Airport / Street Pickups: Tag these rides with your in-app wallets
â€¢ E-receipts: Get your trip itinerary with payment details, right in your inbox
â€¢ Safety: In Case of Emergency, an ICE alert system to send SMS with location details to 2 registered numbers and call option to police hotline
â€¢ Feedback: Rate the trip or shout for experience
â€¢ Best offers: Right in the app to save maximum on your trips
Stay up to date on all our exciting offers and latest happenings by connecting with us online
â€¢ Follow us on Twitter - https://twitter.com/Merucabs
â€¢ Like our Facebook page - https://www.facebook.com/MeruCabs
Got questions? Visit our Ultimate guide on website (https://www.meru.in/customer-support/faqs) for more information or write to us at feedback@meru.in

title: GPS Compass for Android: Map & Navigation
description:
GPS Compass for Android
is a smart compass free with map and gps navigation most easy, intuitive, usefull and simple to use. It allows you to convert your phone/tablet into a handy smart compass using device sensors compass. My compass app is a tool to search bearings (azimuth, directions) using embedded magnetic sensors.
GPS Compass for Android
provides the direction information in both analog, and digital formats with a beautiful user interface. The magnetic sensors are used to provide the direction information. The GPS values are used to provide the speed, and the altimeter data. The current location can be viewed in this digital compass app.
GPS compass for Android
app can be used in your daily outdoor activities. If you are a scout or you are just going to travel or camping, this is a smart digital compass that should be on your phone/tablet and should be used everytime you need a smart compass free.
Download GPS Compass for Android now

- Digital gps compass with Google map
- Simple to use, use it like a real compass
- Professional design

- Magnetic and true north are available, the app automatically takes care of variation.
- The direction information are available.
- GPS is used to provide the speedometer, and the altimeter values.
- The current location is known through the GPS information.
- True North (Default) or Magnetic North.
- GPS Location (address, latitude, longitude).

Orientation sensor is a hardware within a phone. If orientation sensor is not found message is shown, then no compass will work on your phone. It is not our app fault, it is your phone fault.

1. Hold your smart phone flat.
2. Turn your phone horizontally as the arrow overlaps the red double parallel lines, and check the red edge of the arrow point zero degree(0'N) otherwise the red edge could point south, then red edge points north, right side points east, left side points west and down side points south.
ðŸ”” Language ðŸ””
GPS Compass for Android supports the following languages: English, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, Indonesian, German and French ..

title: Tsavaari - Official App of Hyderabad Metro Rail
description:
The Only Travel App You Will Need in Hyderabad - TSavaari App
Enjoy high class comfort and travel safely as you commute via Hyderabad Metro Rail (HMR). No more long queues in front of ticket counters, or bad weather woes, HMR will transform the way you travel in Hyderabad via public transport. Be it sun or rain, any day of the week, you are sure to reach your destination on time as long as you choose to travel with Hyderabad Metro Rail (HMR). Well connected to major locations in Hyderabad, including schools, colleges and offices, with a host of associated travel options (MMTS, TSRTC buses, OLA cabs and autos, local autos and e-Bikes) providing last mile connectivity, HMR is your end-to-end travel partner.
Save time and money as you choose to travel by Hyderabad Metro Rail (HMR)
To make your travel experience stress free, we bring to you the TSavaari App that is designed to cater to all your travel related needs. Plan your travel options even before you hit the streets! TSavaari is a free online, local travel management App by L&T Metro Rail (Hyderabad) Ltd. It is a travel itinerary organizer App that will assist you to commute to any location in Hyderabad using a host of transport options. Available modes of transport will be appended depending on infrastructure availability.
Eco-friendly and green mode of public transport
Heavy traffic and pollution are major concerns for commuters in Hyderabad. Passengers will be able to successfully combat these hazards when they choose to adopt Hyderabad Metro Rail as their preferred type of transportation. Students, professionals, young and old, will be able to travel hassle free, thanks to the â€˜all in oneâ€™ travel App, TSavaari. Now you can plan your travel details with approximate cost and time indicator on the App. Simple to use and amazingly fast, TSavaari App is the best travel management App.
With TSavaari App, your travel options in Hyderabad are always at your fingertips. Whatâ€™s more, it is absolutely free to use. Just download the TSavaari App from Google Play Store or iOS App store and get started. Share the App with your family and friends and spread the word today!
Features
TSavaari App is available for free on iOS Store and Android Play Store.
Know Your Metro: Hyderabad Metro Rail is the worldâ€™s largest public-private partnership (PPP) project, in the Metro rail sector, that will improve the overall socio-economic infrastructure of Hyderabad. State-of-the-art architecture and design aesthetics are the benchmarks of this project.
Journey Planner: Plan your journey in Hyderabad with TSavaari App. It will provide details such as approximate fare, distance, number of stations and interchanges on any route. TSavaari will help you to locate your nearest Metro station using route information module. The planner has many travel options, including Hyderabad Metro Rail, local autos, OLA cabs & auto, MMTS and TSRTC buses. In-App OLA integration allows you to book a ride from and to any Metro train station within seconds and continue your journey beyond to your destination.
Buy A Card: You can buy a smart card directly via the TSavaari App and get it delivered to your residential address for a nominal delivery charge. Alternatively, you can also collect it on your way from nearest Metro station.
My Orders: This screen will display all the orders that you have placed using the TSavaari App so that you can keep track of your expenditure.

title: Rail Jankari - Indian Rail Info, PNR Status & Live
description:
Rail Jankari is an Indian Railways application. It acts as a one stop solution for your railway related queries. Grab this app and get information on the go!
A must have app for all train travelers in India!
â˜… What does Rail Jankari offer?
â— PNR Enquiry & Tracking - Check PNR status as well as save it for future reference. Auto PNR tracking notifies you when current status changes. Rail Jankari also tracks incoming messages with PNR and adds those PNR's automatically to status tracking list.
â— Train Schedule - Detailed schedules & route map of all trains, timings, stops, distance etc. You can also save it for offline usage.
â— Search Trains - Any train. Any Date. Search almost all type of trains between stations and get seat availability, train schedule, running info, coach position and more.
â— Train Running Status - Real time running information of trains, now with tracking on map. You can save it for offline usage.
â— Station Status - Live status of all trains arriving and departing at a station within 2-9 hrs.
â— Seat Availability - Choose your preferred train, Rail Jankari shows you seat availability up to 4 months of all classes at one place with one click.
â— Fare Enquiry - Detailed imposed charges for railway reservation of different classes. All class fares at one click.
â— Refund Calculator - Suggestive refund calculator to give you an idea about the cancellation charges and refund amount.
â— Current Booking - Current booking availability in trains from a station within 4 hrs of departure. Shows all classes availability at once.
â— Coach Layout - Seating arrangement layout of various coaches.
â— Cancelled Trains - Fully and partially cancelled trains.
â— Diverted Trains - Detailed information of all diverted trains.
â— Rescheduled Trains - Detailed information of all rescheduled trains along with delay and expected arrival.
â— Special Trains - Detailed information of all special event trains along with days & timings.
â— Heritage Trains - Detailed information of all heritage trains plying amidst important stations.
â— External Links - Links to IRCTC, NTES and other important web pages.
â— Saved Data - One stop hub for all our saved data. View/delete at one place.
â— Settings - Place to tweak the application with quick inputs, tracking and update check intervals, sound effects etc.
â˜… Key Features
âœ” Material design, easy to use UI.
âœ” Auto PNR tracking, notifies you when current status changes. Great, Isn't it?
âœ” Multi-pane layout to show search form, history & saved data in a single flick.
âœ” Route maps with cool animations for current station tracking in Running status.
âœ” Coach position information based of historic data.
âœ” Long press quick inputs to enter stations/trains quickly. Set it from settings!
âœ” Detailed search history for everything you search.
âœ” Detailed fare breakdown information. All class fares of a train on a single tap.
âœ” Shows via stations when direct train is not available.
âœ” Save PNR status, train schedules and running status for offline usage.
âœ” 20+ color themes. The first and the only themed Indian Railways application.
âœ” Rich eye-catching xxxhdpi ready layouts with reference to android design guidelines
âœ” Free Wi-Fi availability information.
âœ” More features on the way ..
â˜… A Brief Note To The Users
We â™¥ to stay connected with our users. If you have any feedback, questions or concerns, please email us at: railjankari@gmail.com
If you come across any bugs/issues, we request you to help us make the application better by reporting bugs/issues via e-mail. Suggestions/Feature requests are welcome.
â˜… Disclaimer
Rail Jankari is not affiliated to Indian Railways. You are responsible for any legal implications that may arise from such usage. This application serves as a tool to show publicly available information. Please read the complete "Terms of use" in application under App Info.

title: Chennai Local Train Timetable
description:
This app provides information about Chennai suburban/local train services running between two train stations at or after a given time of day.
You can search train services between any two stations which fall on the same direct route either on Weekdays or Sundays, including Velacherry-Beach-Tiruttani and Velacherry-Beach-Sullurupeta routes.
The search provides you with a list of trains with boarding time at source station and alighting time at destination stations.
You can tap on any listed train to get full information about that specific train, like its start/in between/destination stations and time for each.
The App interface supports Tamil, Hindi and English languages.
Among other features:
- You have an option to search nearby source/destination station based on phones last known Geo-coordinates (latitude/longitude)
- An option to long tap on any station name to see it on online maps
- Look at the various routes on which suburban trains operate in Chennai
- Swap Source-Destination stations so as to find return trains easily
- Type Source-Destination station names
- The last searched station pair gets saved for quick use in future
- Live train information
This app can work completely offline.
If an internet connection is available it would be used to only display advertisements and collect usage statistics. This app does not collect any personal information.

title: TSRTC Official Online Booking
description:
Telangana RTC is proud to introduce VAJRA MINI BUS Booking and Inter City / Inter State services to book through mobile / online booking APP at your finger tips.
TSRTC is committed to provide consistently high quality of services and to continuously improve the services through a process of teamwork for the utmost satisfaction of the passengers and to attain a position of pre-eminence in the Bus Transport sector.
Till now, bus passengers bound for various places in the State, had to travel long distances in the City from their places of residence to Bus Stations like MGBS, JBS, Dilsukhnagar to board buses to their destinations.
To reduce the burden of travel within the City and to provide bus facility nearer to their door steps, Mini AC Buses are introduced to provide direct bus facility from various colonies in Hyderabad to Warangal and Nizamabad and back.
Several boarding points (144) have been identified in Hyderabad city other than the regular pick up points at MGBS and JBS, 46 in Warangal & 29 Nizamabad.  Each boarding point is accessible to many surrounding colonies.
A total of 60 trips daily are being run on Hyderabad-Warangal route and 36 trips on Hyderabad-Nizamabad route. The buses are being operated at a frequency of about one hour from the identified origin points in Hyderabad, Warangal and Nizamabad.
Salient Features of Mini AC bus Services (VAJRA):
1. These buses have a seating capacity of 21.
2. These buses are provided with following passenger amenities
i) Comfortable luxury seats with push back facility.
ii) Mobile charging facility.
iii) Air Suspension system in the rear facilitating comfortable journey.
iv) A state-of-art LCD TV with high class audio system.
v) Drinking water bottles and dispensable head seat covers..
The buses are fitted with a mobile device with GPS. Online real time bus tracking facility is extended to the passengers who have booked the tickets.
SMS alert is sent to the reserved passengers besides mail to the email id.

title: GPS Tracker by FollowMee
description:
GPS Tracker by FollowMee converts your Android devices into a GPS tracking device. Installing this mobile app to the device that you want to track, you can monitor its whereabouts when you login to the
FollowMee.com
web site. Using this app,Â  you can track your family members, company devices, or even your employees.
FEATURES:
* Location Monitor
Simply login to the FollowMee.com web site in your desktop or mobile browser. You can view last known location for free. Geofencing, location reporting, location sharing, and other tracking services are available on the web site.
* Data Privacy
We don't serve ad in this mobile app or on the FollowMee.com web site. We don't share your data with outside parties.
* Configurable App Settings
You can configure tracking interval, tracking schedule, or even a password protected lock screen. Business users can use MDM to deploy this app and its settings to the remote devices.
* Tracking Multiple Devices
You can track multiple devices in your account, including devices of other mobile platforms. All your devices are shown on the same map.
* Real-Time Update
By default, this app tracks every 10 minutes. You can adjust this interval on the app settings screen.
* On-Demand Update Remotely
On the FollowMee.com web site, you can send a command to this mobile app to force a location update.
* Full-time Vehicle Tracking Device Setting
Enable this setting and convert your phone into a vehicle tracking device. Tracking starts when the vehicle is driven, and pauses when it is stopped.
* Opt-in Sharing
Your location data is protected by your account credential. But you can opt-in to share your location through a URL. You can also embed your map on your web site.
* No-Internet Contingency
Cellular or Wifi connection is required to upload location data to the FollowMee server. When connection is interrupted, the app continue to track and data is saved in the device storage. When connection resumes, data is then uploaded. After that, your map will show up-to-dateÂ data.
For explanation of required app permissions, see this link: http://www.followmee.com/m/FAQ.aspx#androidpermission

b'"Train Enquiry\xe2\x80\x8b " is a unique train app for \xe2\x80\x9cLive train running status, Booking train tickets,
PNR status, Search train, station status, Seat availability & all other train information in one
light-weight rail app.

Main Feature

PNR STATUS

- Updated PNR station list
- Get PNR status, receive automatic status updates and travel reminders.
- PNR sharing

TRAIN RUNNING STATUS

- Check train running status for all trains anytime, anywhere.
- Share Live Train Status or Location with friends and family

TRAIN SEAT AVAILABILITY & BOOKING

- Find information on trains running between any two stations including fare and real-time
seat availability info.
- Book your Indian Rail tickets directly on IRCTC via the railway app.

SEARCH TRAIN BETWEEN STATION

-Find trains between any two stations
-Get availability and fare


Tips to Use the App

- No need to remember train names or numbers. Search can be done using train number or
name(partial or complete) on all the pages.

- Swipe the Home Screen left and right to access more information.

- No need need to remember Indian railways station names. Auto complete option available.

title: Incredible India
description:
Incredible India App is an innovative project of Ministry of Tourism to assist the international and domestic tourist to showcase India as a holistic destination, revolving around major experiences such as spirituality, heritage, adventure, culture, yoga , wellness and more.
The mobile app has been designed keeping in mind the preferences of the modern traveller. The app follows the trends and technologies of international standards and has been equipped with features to assist the traveller in each phase of their journey to India.

Akbar Travels, one of Indiaâ€™s largest travel companies, is a one stop solution for all your travel needs. title: Indian Rail Guide
description:
Indian Rail Guide is a complete travel companion app for the frequent travellers of Indian Railways. With Indian Railway Guide, you can access train ticket status (PNR enquiry), train timetable, train live running information (train enquiry), train seat availability, train fare, train arrivals/departures at a station and much more from your mobile. Indian Railway Guide app has the following train enquiry features,
1. Store your train tickets using PNR and access them even when you are offline!
2. Receive automatic updates to your mobile whenever your ticket status changes. No more manual checking of wait-listed tickets!
3. Find train schedule using train number or train name
4. Find trains between two railway stations
5. Get train schedule (with offline access) and current running status of any train
6. Get a list of trains arriving/departing from a station in the next 2, 4 or 8 hours!
7. Get the current running status of any train including its location on the Google map
8. Train fare enquiry
9. Train seat availability enquiry (including tatkal)
10. Get schedule of special trains operated by Indian Railways
11. Get a list of rescheduled, cancelled and diverted trains
12. Get train seat layout/birth map
13. Book train tickets using mobile web
14. You can receive automatic updates as a train passes through various stations (Track your train)
15. Use homepage widgets for tracking trains or train tickets. You can even configure tracking widgets on lock screen!
16. Share your train ticket details over sms, email etc.
Following are some of the unique features of Indian Rail Guide,
â˜… Intelligent and power efficient automatic live tracking of trains and PNR ticket status. It is possible to automatically track location of a running train up to every 5 minutes!
â˜… We do not ask for any kind of special device permissions.
â˜… Intelligent offline support for most features so that you can use the app even when there is no network connection. We are in the process of improving this feature.
â˜… Uses multiple online rail databases. You can use either the PRS version or the All (NTES) version.
â˜… Supports all trains operated by Indian Railways including passenger trains, MEMU, EMU, DMU, suburban trains, holiday special trains, MMTS, suvidha, mail express trains and luxury trains.
Disclaimer: This app is not affiliated to indian railways or irctc. This is only a tool to access publicly available information.

title: Govinda - Tirumala Tirupati
description:
Govinda - Tirumala Tirupati Devasthanams app provides services to devotees of Lord Sri Venkateswara, Tirumala. A pilgrim can avail services like Accommodation, Special Entry Darshanam, Hundi, Seva and can be involved in various trusts and schemes that are part of Tirumala Tirupati Devasthanams.
The new App aims to provide pilgrims with better user experience in availing the Services. Pilgrim registration with valid e-mail ID is a prerequisite for booking of Seva/Accommodation/Darshanam . Registration OTP will be sent to the registered mobile number for verification & activation. Please complete all this process well in advance to avail online services.

title: RAIL SAARTHI - INDIAN RAILWAYS OFFICIAL APP
description:
Single window interface for Indian Railway Mobile Applications. Currently there are multiple mobile applications by Indian Railways to cater  various passenger requirements Including on board cleaning. Most of the app cater to one service. To use different services , users need to search and download each application separately.  In order to provide better customer experience, there is a need for integrated application which will give a single window interface for these services.
This app integrates various apps and provide additional features and fulfills Railways commitment towards providing better services. It provides end to end solution to our esteemed passenger from planning of journey to giving their feedback after completion of journey.

title: Rail Beeps
description:
Gone are the days of standing in long railway enquiry queues at the railway stations or be bugged by hearing the constant engaged tone when dialing the Indian Railway Enquiry Office. Now all crucial rail information can be easily availed from the comfort of your mobile phones.
NDTV Rail Beeps mobile app is your single stop for all train information. It provides the latest, fastest updates on reservations (PNR status) and helps you track over 12,000 trains with the latest information on delays. It also helps you discover what train works best for your schedule.
By using NDTV Rail Beeps, you can easily sort out trains by departure times, price and fastest routes. It helps you organise multiple trips at one go. NDTV Rail Beeps search will bring right in front of your mobile screen, the details of the number of trains running, operative days of the trains, train timings and a lot many more options. The simple NDTV Rail Beeps is based on real-time data from the Indian Railways with results that are constantly updated.
The NDTV Rail Beeps app helps you check the Live Train Status or the Train Running Status of all Indian Railways trains. This is one of the fastest ways to get latest information and spot your train in real time. You can find extensive details - the current location of your train, its late status, the platform number it arrives on and expected time of arrival and departure. With the use of accurate GPS tracker and navigation system, this vital information is made available to the passengers for a hassle-free travelling experience.
The PNR status gives the booking status of your ticket and provides vital information on whether the ticket has been confirmed, is on waiting list (WL) or is under reservation against cancellation (RAC). Checking PNR status on NDTV Rail Beeps is easy. Simply enter your PNR number on the search bar and it will reflect the PNR status of your ticket.
There are a large number of trains that run across the country every day. NDTV Rail Beeps helps you see trains between two stations at your command. It makes the entire process of finding where to travel, how to travel and when to travel, very simple. Under the â€˜Trains Between Two Stationsâ€™ tab, there are two search boxes. Enter the names of the two stations you want to check the status between. When you write the name of the station, a drop-down menu will provide you with one or more options of the station name and the station code. Just select the stations you want and submit your query. The results will show you number of trains running between the two selected stations, Indian Railway train codes/ train numbers, train names, the train station of origin, scheduled departure time, the weekly schedule of the trains and the travel classes.
Be assured, NDTV Rail Beeps is a hassle-free information source for all your railway enquiries. Simply install and access the world of Indian Railways at your fingertips.

title: Mobike - Smart Bike Sharing
description:
Mobike is the worldâ€™s first and largest dockless, cash-free bike share platform. With Mobike you can get around your city easily with no need to get stuck in traffic, park your bike at stations far away, or even own a bike.
Whether youâ€™re going to work or riding for fun, Mobike is there for every occasion. Whenever you need one, find a Mobike near you, unlock it, and youâ€™re good to go!
Download the app to begin your first ride today!
Riding with Mobike is easy. Hereâ€™s how it works:
- Open the app and find a Mobike nearby on the map
- Tap on a Mobike to find directions to it. You can also reserve it for 15 minutes to make sure you have time to get to the bike you want.
- When you find your Mobike, unlock it by scanning the QR code on the lock thatâ€™s attached to the top of the rear wheel or the middle of the handlebar.
- Once unlocked, enjoy the two-wheeled ride to your destination. Ride safe!
- Once youâ€™re done riding, park at any public bicycle parking spot, rack, or Mobike Preferred Location (MPL).
- Lock the bike by sliding the lock and see your trip details pop up immediately.
- Enjoy the rest of your day knowing you saved a little more time and money.
Have a question about Mobike? Visit mobike.com

title: Auto Tatkal - IRCTC Train Ticket Booking
description:
Thanks for supporting our app. We have released a new Chrome Extension. Please check it at this link:   http://bit.ly/autofillext
âœ” Autofill support for both IRCTC Rail Connect app and Website
âœ” It is 100% free and do not charge any additional commission.
âœ” Please share it with your friends and family, if you like it.
âœ” It is easy to use with a very simple and intuitive UI.
âœ” Indian Railway Train Ticket Booking on IRCTC Rail Connect & Website made Smarter, Faster & Easier.
âœ” It is the best Rail / Train Tatkal Ticket Booking Application/Software which speeds up the process of getting a confirmed ticket for you without compromising on your berth/coach preference.
âœ” This is the Fastest Ticket Booking App for IRCTC rail connect and website which can book tickets under 25 - 35 Seconds.
âœ” Auto Tatkal helps you save time for all of the above process by autofilling all the details for booking in IRCTC forms and gives you an edge over other users booking a ticket, which increases your probability of getting a ticket.
Features offered:
Smart Ticket Booking
âœ”  Automated Ticket Booking (Enhanced Automated Online Form Filling)
âœ”  All data except captchas will be auto filled by this application,
âœ”  Book your Train ticket in a faster and convenient way from your mobile / tablet
âœ”  Save Time and book tickets faster even during Tatkal Hours
âœ”  Saves Trip details for future use
âœ”  Need not remember your IRCTC rail connect and website username & password, just save your Login credentials in app and book tickets in just 3 clicks
âœ”  Local Storage of payment method,login credentials
âœ”  Enter two Captchas and Thats it, Auto Tatkal takes care of everything else.
âœ”  All the stations names, Bank names are available in the app itself. Just select them by using auto complete feature while filling the details.
AdBlocking & Image / JS / CSS caching
âœ” Ad Blocking - Blocks Ads/Unwanted Images on IRCTC rail connect and website for Faster Loading
âœ” Optimized the pages / activities of IRCTC rail connect and website on app to save data costs of user.
âœ” Many of the website images, javascript & css files are stored / cached in app
âœ” Images & file caching saves data costs as well as increases booking speed.
âœ” It also enables the app work well even in low network speed.
Instructions for use:
âœ”  Create a new form by clicking on the "New Form" button.
âœ” Fill all the information you need and click on the save icon on the top right corner of the page.
âœ” You can also initiate the booking by clicking on the book now link on the right corner of the page. Doing so, auto saves the form.
âœ” Once the browser is opened all the details that you have entered in the form will be autofilled.
âœ” Autofill payment option is added for all major payment modes supported by www.irctc.co.in including Debit/Credit Cards,Netbanking and Payment Gateway services (PayTM / ITZ / PayU)
âœ” Super Speed IRCTC rail connect and website mobile Tatkal Ticket Booking Ever supported by www.irctc.co.in
âœ” You can leave this fields blank if you don't want your payment details to be saved, you can enter the details during checkout on IRCTC  rail connect and website once all the other details are autofilled by the app and you reaches the payment.
For FAQ refer to: https://autotatkal.wordpress.com/
This app is not affiliated to Indian Railway in any manner. Credentials and Passenger info is saved only locally in the user device which can be deleted by the end user at any point of time. In case you have any suggestions/complaints please reach us at livetv24x7online@gmail.com or use Feedback feature in the App.
AutoTatkal fills the Travel booking details in IRCTC Rail connect and website automatically using pre saved details and lets the user focus on filling CAPTCHA and payment details only.

title: Metro ( Delhi & Mumbai) and Bus Tickets & Passes
description:
Ridlr is a public transport ticketing and commuting app thatâ€™s apt for your daily intra-city travel needs. Get rid of queues and hassles of carrying change by buying your DMRC Airport line Metro Ticket, Mumbai Metro (SKIIIP) tickets, BEST Mumbai bus tickets, NMMT AC bus tickets, MBMT bus tickets on select routes as well as recharging your BEST pass, Mumbai metro smart card using the Ridlr app.
You can also get timetable for Metro, Local Trains, Monorail, BEST and NMMT buses in Mumbai. Stay informed about multiple modes of transport, with route display on the map. Plan your commute with traffic updates and alerts about delays, cancellations, mega blocks, etc. directly on your smart phone.
App Highlights - Go Cashless. No more queues :
1) DMRC - Single Journey Mobile Ticketing
- Buy your Single Journey on the mobile. Just scan and go
2) Reliance Mumbai Metro - Mobile ticketing and Smart Card Recharge
- Buy your Single Journey, Return Journey, Trip Pass and Stored Value pass on the mobile. Just scan and go!
- Recharge your Mumbai Metro smart card with a few simple steps on Ridlr app
- Get Mumbai Metro train timetable, routes and map; even when you are offline
3) BEST Ticketing â€“ BEST Bus Tickets and Pass Recharge
-  Book your BEST bus tickets using Ridlr, and get rid of all hassles related to change. Also reward your daily travel with rewards and cashback. Now available in all BEST Mumbai buses, AC or non AC.
- Recharge your BEST bus pass using Ridlr, and get rid of the pain of standing in queues. Both, monthly mobile bus pass and daily pass available
4) NMMT Bus Mobile Tickets
- Get rid of the hassles of carrying change! Now book your NMMT AC bus tickets (all routes) with Ridlr app now
- Get NMMT bus route maps and timings to check and plan your commute
5) MBMT Bus Mobile Tickets

title: Live Train Running Status
description:
App Features highlights:
Live Running Status
Live Station Enquiry
PNR Check
Seat Availability Check
Train Between Stations
Train Schedule
Rescheduled Trains
Cancelled Trains
Diverted Trains
Coach Layout
Trains affected by Fog
Running Status(Delayed Trains) with detailed Live Status
Rescheduled Trains
Cancelled Trains
Rail Email
Live Running Status:
Just enter the train name or number in the search box of the app and autocomplete will help you in completing name/number. select and get summarized live IRCTC/NTES train status and information anytime, anywhere. Select a different date from floating menu or refresh the status. Search history contains route information also. Click one from history list for one click search.
Live Station Enquiry:
Enter Station Code/Name, Autocomplete will help you in completing the station name/code. Chose via station and duration(time within next 2,4,6 or 8 hrs) and simply click on get trains. The list contains required information. The via station is optional, you can let it empty. Click on train number will show the live status of that particular train for the date it started on. Click one from history list for one click search.
PNR Check:
Enter the PNR number, get the latest status of PNR. Clicking on PNR number(In available Previous/Upcoming list) will refresh the PNR. Clicking on Train number will show you the live running status.
Seat Availability Check
Check for the seat availability just with a few clicks. Autocomplete will help in station names. Select start date and click on get Trains. The new screen will have a list of trains with the classes, clicking on a class will get the availability in the train for next 6 days and the fare too.
Train Between Stations:
Search for trains between stations( Direct as well as via different station). The list show direct trains separately. Via trains list shows Trains  from source to Via station and Via station to Destination station. Click one from history list for one click search.
Train Schedule:
To check train schedule must switch the button off which is there live train page. switching it off will check the button name to get Schedule. Simple enter the train number /name, or select from the autocomplete suggestion list and it will get the data and display.
Rescheduled/Cancelled/Diverted Trains:
List of IRCTC/NTES trains which is rescheduled/Cancelled/Diverted. Filter it by date or type or search from in the list. Refresh the list from floating menu. Canceled trains have two separate lists, Fully canceled and Partially canceled.
Trains affected by Fog:
List of trains affected by fog. It has delayed trains, rescheduled and canceled(fully and partially). The floating menu can be used to refresh or filter the list. The delayed trains also have full view of its running status, by clicking on the individual train from the list.
*************************************************
Rail Email:
First of its Kind, Rail Email: Get all your Email tickets right in the app from Gmail IRCTC account new and improved UI, Advanced progress bar
*******************************************************
Dissimilar:
Please Note: The app is privately maintained and does not have any affiliation whatsoever to Indian Railways or NTES or IRCTC. Data provided by the app are just for Information Purpose. Information available here is collected from various sources and are subjected to change without any prior information. We value the source of information and maintain professional ethics. You are requested to re-verify it from other official sources.

title: GOAMILES
description:
"GOA MILES", as the name suggests is exclusively for State of GOA. We bring you the most simplest way to give you a relaxing way of booking taxi when you arrive in state of GOA. This is GTDC (Goa Tourism Development Corporation) Application approved with government rates of plying in the state of GOA.
You enjoy the beaches of Goa with thumb swipe on your smartphone to book the taxi on demand & make your journey the way you want - anytime â€“ anywhere. An array of vehicles choices for you to select best suited to your need available at your disposal. "GOA MILES" taxis are calibrated as per the Government rate card.
Enjoy your holidays & Pay securely online and load balance in your GOA MILES Balance so you never need cash on hand.- Know exactly how far away your stop is. You can also track the taxi and time your travel accordingly.- Sit back, relax, and reach your destination. we will take care of your travel.
Class of Vehicles you can enjoy & relax:
â€¢	Sedan: Book the cheapest AC taxi in town starting with best in class offers
â€¢	Hatchback: Travel in comfy AC hatchbacks at pocket-friendly fares, Enjoy your ride
â€¢	SUV: For bigger space and Bigger enjoyment, enjoy our SUV for large space & Size to accommodate you & your family
â€¢	SUV Classic: Rest assured to get best in class drivers to enjoy even bigger space & hospitality with our highly trained drivers to make your ride a memorable one.
All our vehicles comes with pre training programs for drivers & drivers are being trained to make your journey a memorable one. We provide an inbuilt Emergency - "PANIC" button in your app to make sure that in spite of best driver training we do not take any chances with the safety of our passengers.
Book a cab in just a few taps. Hereâ€™s how it works:
â€¢	Set your pickup location (E.g. Home, Office, Airport, Railway station, current location, etc.)
â€¢	Set your Drop Location (E.g. Home, Office, Airport, Railway station, to be dropped) location, etc
â€¢	See all available cabs/taxis near your location being displayed on the map
â€¢	Multiple ways to pay: Pay Digitally for your trips in cash or via multiple cashless options like ONLINE (Debit, Credit, BHIM, UPI)
â€¢	Pick the type of vehicle you want & tap â€˜CONFIRMâ€™
â€¢	You will be able to see the type of vehicle along with the rates for your easy selection and opt for best suit
â€¢	Get instant confirmation with trip details like Driver, Vehicle number, Type of Vehicle and the OTP to be given to driver in the app itself
â€¢	Track your cab in real time with Arrival time and Drop time when you give OTP to driver
â€¢	Invoices history can be seen immediately in â€œMY RIDESâ€ after you finish your trip & previous trips would be stored below the current one
â€¢	Know Fares & Ride features: Check fares & various features of a ride category before booking
â€¢	Share:  Share the ride details with your near & dear ones
We hope you find the features valuable & enjoy the benefits as much as we enjoyed making it for you. we are more than happy to receive any request for further improvisation.
Got questions? Visit "GOA MILES" support at support@goamiles.com  or get help section with www.goamiles.com/help

You enjoy the beaches of Goa with thumb swipe on your smartphone to book the taxi on demand & make your journey the way you want - anytime \xe2\x80\x93 anywhere. An array of vehicles choices for you to select best suited to your need available at your disposal. "GOA MILES" taxis are calibrated as per the Government rate card.
Enjoy your holidays & Pay securely online and load balance in your GOA MILES Balance so you never need cash on hand.- Know exactly how far away your stop is. You can also track the taxi and time your travel accordingly.- Sit back, relax, and reach your destination. we will take care of your travel.
Class of Vehicles you can enjoy & relax:
\xe2\x80\xa2\tSedan: Book the cheapest AC taxi in town starting with best in class offers
\xe2\x80\xa2\tHatchback: Travel in comfy AC hatchbacks at pocket-friendly fares, Enjoy your ride
\xe2\x80\xa2\tSUV: For bigger space and Bigger enjoyment, enjoy our SUV for large space & Size to accommodate you & your family
\xe2\x80\xa2\tSUV Classic: Rest assured to get best in class drivers to enjoy even bigger space & hospitality with our highly trained drivers to make your ride a memorable one.

All our vehicles comes with pre training programs for drivers & drivers are being trained to make your journey a memorable one. We provide an inbuilt Emergency - "PANIC" button in your app to make sure that in spite of best driver training we do not take any chances with the safety of our passengers.

Book a cab in just a few taps. Here\xe2\x80\x99s how it works:

\xe2\x80\xa2\tSet your pickup location (E.g. Home, Office, Airport, Railway station, current location, etc.)
\xe2\x80\xa2\tSet your Drop Location (E.g. Home, Office, Airport, Railway station, to be dropped) location, etc
\xe2\x80\xa2\tSee all available cabs/taxis near your location being displayed on the map
\xe2\x80\xa2\tMultiple ways to pay: Pay Digitally for your trips in cash or via multiple cashless options like ONLINE (Debit, Credit, BHIM, UPI)
\xe2\x80\xa2\tPick the type of vehicle you want & tap \xe2\x80\x98CONFIRM\xe2\x80\x99

\xe2\x80\xa2\tGet instant confirmation with trip details like Driver, Vehicle number, Type of Vehicle and the OTP to be given to driver in the app itself

title: Live Train Status, Confirm Train Seat & PNR Status
description:
"MyRailgadi" is a unique train app for all your Indian Railway and train enquiry
Live Status : Live train status, Live station status along with live locals.
Reservation : Train schedule, Train between station, PNR Status with confirm predictions, Seat
availability along with confirm chances and alternatives, Seat availability calendar, Trains by station, Fare
calculator, Refund calculator.
Travel Guide: Seat map, Coach Layout, Platform locator, Speedometer, Nearest station, Clean my
coach.
Check out more highlights of the MyRailgadi App
Train seat availability
- Check seat availability with confirm chances.
- Also discover all possible alternatives to book conferm ticket train ticket.
Live train status, station & locals
- Check train running status by just providing train number. This app features GPS based Train Status with real time speed of the train.
- Get live station and locals status with real time location of train in a single click.
PNR status & prediction
- Check current PNR status as well as confirm chances in a single click.
- MyRailgadi Auto PNR tracking notifies you when current status changes.
Reservation enquiry
- See train schedule for all Indian rail passenger and express trains.
- PNR prediction for waitlisted tickets.
- See the arrival & departure of trains by station
- Know Fare for all classes and also calculate exactly how much refund you are eligible for on ticket
cancellation
.
Travel guide
- Know your train coach layout and seat map before you get board.
- Make sure you are on right platform on which the train is scheduled to arrive using Platform locator
feature.
- Curios to know the train speed, go to speedometer and check the real time speed of the train.
- Searching nearby station is now under your fingertip, just visit to Nearby station and find station
nearby you according to your range.
Disclaimer : Train Seat Availability - Indian Railway PNR & IRCTC Info is not affiliated with IRCTC,
NTES or Indian Railways and there are no warranties associated with the app. Train Seat Availability
- Indian Railway app relies on public information available on 3rd party websites.

How to find vehicle owner detail:
Type your vehicle's first 6 letters (e.g. MH02) in first box then Like AB in second box and
Now type vehicle Number in third box (e.g. 4321)
Click on "Search" and get details
Owner details:
Check registration details like owner name, vehicle type, Registration date, Engine number, Chassis number, RC/FC expiry, Finance, tax validity etc. of any vehicle without login or Internet anytime anywhere.
This application usefull as vehicle information tracker to find your own city, state vehicle registration
details in a picnic or a tour spot.
You don't need to go to the Regional Transport Office (RTO) to get these details for a car, bike, truck, taxi, scooter or any other Indian Vehicle anymore!
The app can find the RTO registration number verification details for all the states of India.
Andhra Pradesh, Arunachal Pradesh, Assam, Bihar, Chhattisgarh, Delhi, Goa, Gujarat, Haryana, Himachal Pradesh, Jammu and Kashmir, Jharkhand, Karnataka, Kerala, Madhya Pradesh, Maharashtra, Manipur, Meghalaya, Mizoram, Nagaland, Odisha, Punjab, Rajasthan, Sikkim, Tamil Nadu, Telangana, Tripura, Uttar Pradesh, Uttarakhand, West Bengal.
NOTE:
-We are in no way related to RTO VAHAN, VAAHAN Parivahan or any RTO authority in India. This is not an official app of RTO.
-We show information available in public domain only. We do not plan to incorporate phone number or address of users for safety and security purposes.
We hope you will enjoy our app. Thank you.

title: Muslim Prayer Times - Qibla Compass, Azan, Quran
description:
Muslim Prayer Times App with Islamic Compass, Islamic prayers time, Qibla Compass, Qibla Map, Ramadan Times and Hijri Calendar and date converter with holy Mecca Background. You can use this app at any place in the world to find qibla direction accurately. As Ramadan 2018 is going to start from 5-6 Map ,Qibla app will help you to check Salat timing and find qibla direction.
The Qiblah has importance to Muslims salaat and plays a part in different occasions. In the Islam Muslims are buried with the body at right angles to the Qibla and the face turned right towards Qiblah direction.
Ramadan 2019
â€¢ Ramadan 2019 Sehri, Iftar and Imsac Times.
â€¢ Complete Ramadan Calendar 2019
â€¢ Complete Ramzan times month schedule.
Prayer Times:
â€¢ Shows salt times for every day Namaz.
â€¢ Shows Fajr, Sunrise, Dhuhr, Asr, Sunset, Maghrib and Isha Times
â€¢ Alarm and Notification setting for every prayer time.
â€¢ Daylight saving for each prayer.
â€¢ Multiple Azan Sounds.
â€¢ Juristic Methods : Shafii and Hanfi
â€¢ Time Formats : 12-hour, 24-hour
â€¢ Multiple languages to chose.
Qibla in Map:
â€¢ Qibla Finder anywhere on map.
â€¢ Shows mecca distance from your place and location address.
â€¢ MAgnetic filed indicator.
â€¢ Spirit level indicator.
Qibla Compass:
The Qibla is the direction that Muslim should face when doing prays during salat or namaz. It is fixed as the direction of the Kaaba in Mecca.
â€¢ Find Qibla anywhere on the globe are you in.
â€¢ App can use device previous last recorded Location to show mecca direction.
â€¢ It can be use offline.
â€¢ 15 Qibla Compass Themes.
Islamic Date Converter:
â€¢ Get Islamic Calendar 2018.
â€¢ Shows Gregorian and Hijri date.
â€¢ Convert Muslim Calendar date to Gregorian date and vise versa.
â€¢ Hijri Calendar date in Arabic language.
Please, You can give feedback and we would love to listen your suggestions by E-mail & Facebook.
E-mail: ramnsg25@gmail.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TrueIslam
To Set Your Location:
In Many Device, It will ask to enable GPS to get exact location, Using App first time kindly restart app after Enabling GPS
Note:
- As Prayer Direction and Prayer times vary from different part of the world. Make sure first by selecting different Namaz time calculation methods in the setting screen.
- Find Qibla direction by using device on a flat surface to get accurate result. Make sure there is not any electromagnetic field and metal objects close to device.
Your use of Muslim Prayer Times - Qibla Compass, Azan, Quran is free of charge in exchange for safely using some of your device's resources (WiFi and very limited cellular data), and only when you are not using your device. You may turn this off from the settings menu. Please see our TOS for further information. http://quranmp3app.com/privacy/ramadan2018

title: Where Am I?
description:
View your current location and its details on your Android phone using Where Am I? app. This is very useful when you are in a new location or traveling.
User can get many other useful details :
1. Address
2. Lat & Long
Added features :
- You can share the location with latitude and longitude
- You can copy the location with latitude and longitude
User can customize his/her location by selecting the location on Map OR entering the address.
Also can calculate the distance between current location and target location Or any two locations.
Keywords : Where AM I?, Where I AM?, Track Me, Get Location, Location, Navigation, Latitude and Longitude, Lat and Long, Find Location, My location, My GPS, GPS location

title: Fast Book- Tatkal Ticket IRCTC
description:
Fast Book-Tatkal Ticket IRCTC is the best Complete Rail Information App / Tatkal/General Ticket Booking Application/Software which speeds up the process of getting a confirmed ticket for you without compromising on your berth/coach preference.
This is the Fastest Ticket Booking App for IRCTC which can book tickets faster provided that you have high speed internet connectivity, When you try to book a tatkal ticket from your mobile, most of the time is spent on filling in details like Source,Destination,Date,Selecting Train,Coach,Filling in Passengerand Card /Payment Details. Fast book-Tatkal Ticket IRCTC helps you save time for all of the above process by autofilling all the details for booking in IRCTC forms and gives you an edge over other users booking a ticket, which increases your probability of getting a ticket
The FASTEST Autofill Adblock app in the market to book your train tickets on IRCTC.
ã€Main featuresã€‘
â˜† Automated Ticket Booking
â˜† PNR Status,Live Train Tracking Status,Train Timetable,Cancelled/Rescheduled/Fog Affected Trains,Fare/Seat Availability,Train Arrivals at Station
â˜† Ad Blocking - Blocks Ads/Unwanted Images on IRCTC Webpage for Faster Loading
â˜† Search & Book - Train Between Stations
â˜† Faster Tatkal Ticket Booking
â˜† My Tickets - View all your ticket details without going through SMSes.
â˜† Set Source,Destination,Train Name,Berth Preference,Class and Date of Journey easily
â˜† Easy to Manage Passenger List
â˜† Local Storage of payment method,login credentials
â˜† Platform Status and Coach Information
â˜† Train Rating
â˜† Works with new IRCTC Website
â˜† Now Supports General,Ladies,Lower Berth along with Tatkal and Premium Tatkal
â˜† Automated Ticket Booking (Enhanced Automated Online Form Filling)
All data except captchas will be auto filled by this application, initially you need to enter the captcha on login screen and then click on login button either on the page or a custom button shown above the keyboard
Your Source,Destination Station and Date of journey,Train,Class,Passenger Information will be automatically filled based on the data you have set earlier.
You need to enter the next captcha that appears on the page where passenger information needs to be entered, Enter two Captchas and
Thats it!!!.
â˜† Search & Book
Provide your Source and Destination Station, You will be presented with a list of trains passing through those stations, Click on Book Now under any train and start booking tickets instantaneously.
â˜† Faster Tatkal Ticket Booking
Assists and Helps you in Booking Tatkal Tickets
â˜† My Tickets
Goto My Tickets Option to get details about your ticket,
You Can Easily get your Seat No,PNR,Date Of Journey,Time and Fare
Share Tickets ,Split your Ticket Fare and Berth Information
â˜† Set Source,Destination,Train Name,Berth Preference,Class and Date of Journey easily Offline
You dont need to be connected to internet to enter source,destination or train name. All the stations and train names are available in the app itself. if your train is not listed or is a special train just enter your train number there
Select your class and date of journey for the trip before you start booking.
â˜† Easy to Manage Passenger List
You can add as many passengers to the list as you want with berth preference,age and name. Passengers can also be deleted at anytime, during booking you have the option to select which all passengers are required for booking ticket. Leave a tick mark for the passengers to whom you would like to book ticket and click on proceed rest will be taken care by the app
â˜† Local Storage of payment method,login credentials
You dont need to spent time entering your irctc login credentials or payment details everytime you login to your account or make a payment.you can leave this fields blank if you dont want your payment details to be saved. it supports all payment modes including IRCTC eWallet,Debit/Credit Cards,Netbanking and Payment Gateway
Super Speed IRCTC Mobile Tatkal Ticket Booking Ever

title: Autowala
description:
Aauuuttttooooo....... Now no more shouting's for Auto.
Autowala is a market place for Auto drivers and Auto passengers. Presently launched in India. The Passengers can utilise this app to find Auto's in nearby their location. Now Auto drivers can register themselves for free and get ready for their first smart ride in less then 24 hrs. No more confusions related to auto meter fare. The trip cost is calculated based on passenger's journey in google map and fare charges of auto driver which is displayed before passenger confirm the ride.
Note:- Auto drivers should provide the correct Vehicle Registration Number, Driving License Number and Mobile Number to get registered.
